  "keyFeatures": [
    "Automated scraping of financial data from 18+ institutions using Selenium/Chrome",
    "OFX protocol support for direct bank connections without a browser",
    "Parallel update runner with per-config logging and status tracking",
    "Interactive IPython shell for debugging and manual scraping steps",
    "Persistent Chrome profiles to avoid repeated MFA login flows",
    "Automatic retry with visible browser on headless scraping failures",
    "Designed to integrate with beancount-import for double-entry bookkeeping",
    "Atomic file writes to prevent corrupt output on failures"
  ],
